# 📊 Student Placement Data Analysis (Using Pandas)

This Python script analyzes mock placement data of students to provide key insights like:
- Number of high package offers
- Company-wise placement stats
- Students below certain package thresholds

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Count of students placed with packages above 5 LPA
- 🏢 Total students placed in IBM
- 🔍 List of students with packages below 5 LPA
- 📉 Minimum & 📈 Maximum offered package

